{"tid":1365975,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］如何定義宗教活動？","createTime":"2019-07-25T21:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T21:55:23.000Z","uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f4a3ef9f6a253dc8a420902ac6046afd514608","tid":1365975,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:51:19.000Z","msg":"作為一個自學既佛教徒<br />\n我好想係星期六為元朗巡遊祭天祈福驅妖<br />\n但又好怕警察會誤會我係遊行<br />\n<br />\n有無法律巴打可以俾d意見<br />\n我要做d咩行為先算 宗教活動呢？<br />\n抬埋佛像一齊行得唔得呢？舞龍？飄色巡遊？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n阿彌陀佛<br />\n近日元朗河妖跋扈，鼠輩橫行，正道不彰<br />\n香港各界善眾，齊集元朗誠心禮佛，巡遊祭天<br />\n<br />\n誠心祈求 早日驅除黑邪外道，官差回歸正道。<br />\n<br />\n阿彌陀佛～大慈大悲觀世音菩薩救苦救難救香港～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-"},{"pid":"fd53f1f318227646c898bb8a7657544d176026ff","tid":1365975,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{